</div>
<p class="indent">
  Conditions <a href="#x1-30021">I</a> and <a href="#x1-30032">II</a> can be met after (properly justified) quantitative approximations<span class="footnote-mark"><a href="#fn7x0" id="fn7x0-bk"><sup class="textsuperscript" id="x1-3004f7">[7]</sup></a></span>. The situation which fulfils conditions <a href="#x1-30021">I</a>-<a href="#x1-30032">II</a> will be expressed as
  
