        <mi>C</mi>
      </mrow>
      <mrow>
        <mn>1</mn>
      </mrow>
    </msub>
  </math>, which concerns those aspects which are relevant for the process that is constrained. At the same time,
  
  <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
